{"tid":840813,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"《七芯海棠》調寄 李克勤《戀愛為何物》","createTime":"2018-09-29T05:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T05:36:29.000Z","uid":72696,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"868e51d424c1f532dea9d7dce9542a5424957a69","tid":840813,"uid":72696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"Hello，大家好，小弟纏玉。好耐冇出嚟填詞啦，希望仲有人識得我呢個骨灰級老人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講返先，呢首歌其實已經差唔多成年前開始寫，但係一直未能完成，中間斷斷續續咁又寫啲寫啲咁，所以詞嘅質素就肯定唔慌好得去邊㗎啦。只不過為咗紀念我終於失驚無神通咗關，所以照樣post出嚟，希望大家插得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廢話就講住咁多先，下面進入文字呻吟模式，如果唔鐘意睇我嘅文字，可以直接skip去歌詞嗰度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n紙墨暫擱且怡情，江湖再逢已經年。<br />\n   <br />\n翻看手機備忘錄，仿佛瘙癢恰逢肉裏針，乍見年前未克完成之作，一時痛癢交加，復又搖起筆桿來。<br />\n  <br />\n本已認命，擱筆如落槳，駕舟遁逃詞海汪洋。偏是現世造化弄人，更有甚於文學作品者。此刻靈感仍缺，猶是戰戰兢兢，卻還得狗尾續貂。<br />\n  <br />\n潛游思海，憶昔啟筆之念，感受遂深。金書眾眾，每教落淚者，獨程靈素一人矣。多少年來一直想寫，奈何又懼劣墨難訴衷腸，積埋心底，素成隱願。<br />\n  <br />\n而今洗盡鉛華，受蒼莽世道荼毒至深，反有扔下心頭大石之感，藉石墜心湖的良久震蕩，織成寸縷緒言。<br />\n  <br />\n乃念：詞作孰好孰壞乎，已非我所能司之事。說穿了不過語出摯情，貪其一快罷了。<br />\n  <br />\n咬文嚼字之初衷、描寫抒訴之原委，便也懶談，交諸君自斟酌豈非善哉？<br />\n  <br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。  <br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/134517_92599ce985c99e81c83a2d3b624eb2aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F134517_92599ce985c99e81c83a2d3b624eb2aa.png&h=441e8e27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n《七芯海棠》調寄 李克勤《戀愛為何物》<br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n作曲 : AGA 江海迦<br />\n  <br />\n作詞：張纏玉<br />\n  <br />\n原詞 : 林若寧<br />\n  <br />\n編曲 : 黃思彥<br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n捧一對蠟燭 堆一撮黃土<br />\n  <br />\n色香俱欠缺 擎風中不倒<br />\n  <br />\n在暗自默數 斟酌住濃度<br />\n  <br />\n天荒地老 哪及眼下溫熱懷抱<br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n休失態嚎哭 這感覺還好<br />\n  <br />\n終點不遠矣 尚差些鼓搗<br />\n  <br />\n毒計預備好 譜美夢帶入墳墓<br />\n  <br />\n盼劇毒見效 製造惡敵陪君終老<br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n今世情無路 回頭望悉數是懊惱<br />\n  <br />\n柔情跟癡意絮語永遠難盡訴<br />\n  <br />\n相處有期已很好 緣何乞討<br />\n  <br />\n栽花是為了自醉 沒氣味更願糊塗<br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n此去黃泉路 遺留用心盼被看到<br />\n  <br />\n離愁雖恐怖也算暗證情未老<br />\n  <br />\n殉愛有途也很好 時辰不早<br />\n  <br />\n七芯毒藥暗喻這淡雅若有若無 暗芳自吐<br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n花燭當遺稿 燒光變完好<br />\n  <br />\n兄妹般錯配 從此土歸土<br />\n  <br />\n命葬廟殿草 想也是壯烈無道<br />\n  <br />\n自製著噩耗 化做美麗塵埃飛舞<br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n今世情無路 回頭望悉數是懊惱<br />\n  <br />\n柔情跟癡意絮語永遠難盡訴<br />\n  <br />\n相處有期已很好 緣何乞討<br />\n  <br />\n栽花是為了自醉 沒氣味更願糊塗<br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n此去黃泉路 遺留用心盼被看到<br />\n  <br />\n離愁雖恐怖也算暗證情未老<br />\n  <br />\n殉愛有途也很好 時辰不早<br />\n  <br />\n七芯毒藥暗喻這現眼孽報 未到悟覺已倒數<br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n（靈素此去 陽與陰隔 何世福至 幸與君證相思？）<br />\n  <br />\n哀世情無道⋯⋯<br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n只見前塵路 綿綿未止往事似訴<br />\n  <br />\n惟瀕熄的愛貫注兩臂猶合抱<br />\n  <br />\n只有決堤這一遭 被浸沒更好<br />\n  <br />\n此刻蠟炬已盡化 淚眼便也徒勞 期限已到<br />\n  <br />\n用淚告 請緊記故人程門靈素"},{"pid":"19601d9825388279825fd8c80217389dda9238d1","tid":840813,"uid":40429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"纏玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62538894b8d56e3c6df02685f3d827f57f320803","tid":840813,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:18:06.000Z","msg":"終於有新作<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3992a173fda571f70509918cf441660f51c84db","tid":840813,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:25:16.000Z","msg":"回來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55cd446a6c55269a9a2bf8f81f59178453f5eb3","tid":840813,"uid":72696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3992a173fda571f70509918cf441660f51c84db","tid":840813,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:25:16.000Z","msg":"回來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:33:24.000Z","msg":"轉瞬便即離開"},{"pid":"9402773082209c1f48c42416d1d71c0870733c7c","tid":840813,"uid":72696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19601d9825388279825fd8c80217389dda9238d1","tid":840813,"uid":40429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"纏玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"估到你第一"},{"pid":"82654373a0822e9b7dd7208f5e346d2bafd5e42e","tid":840813,"uid":72696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62538894b8d56e3c6df02685f3d